#

Mushroom Risotto with Truffle Oil and Parmesan

$12.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-Protein

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A creamy, rich risotto infused with earthy mushrooms and a drizzle of luxurious truffle oil.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Mushrooms (cremini or shiitake): 2 cups, sliced
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups, heated
  • Onion: 1, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • White wine: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped (for garnish)
